keep it secret from the united states to offset us pressure to 
free obeid in exchange for western hostages in lebanon 
israeli leaders know that agreeing to such an american request 
would help mend the recent strains in israeliamerican ties but 
they fear that obeids release would prompt criticism at home that 
israel risked the lives of its soldiers for an operation that 
solely benefited america the newspaper said 
